section.p:
The table view can display


subdivision structure: when the school is selected in tree view;

full list of students: when the school is selected in tree view and Show all students button is active in the toolbar (see  );

list of students in a given subdivision: when a subdivision is selected in the tree view;

list of archived students: then the archive is selected in the tree view.

The table view allows you to:


sort the tables on any column by simply clicking on that column header ( );

double click on any row to edit it;

context menus (_fixme_ [xref] are available for every row of the table;

full text search on all fields using filter tool in the toolbar (see  );

filter on any column by entering search string in the fields immediately below the column header; multiple simultaneous filters are also available.



